//
// T032 — R6 attached-comment preservation per formatting-rules.contract.md §6.
//
// Frozen invariants:
//   * trailing line comment stays on the same line as the
//     declaration that precedes it
//   * leading block comment stays immediately above the
//     declaration that follows it
//   * inline comment between two tokens of a single statement
//     (Session 2026-05-05 Q2) preserved byte-for-byte
//
// AUTHORED RED — XFAIL until T051 implements R6.

// XFAIL: *
// RUN: echo 'module m {/* hdr */ reg q[8]; reg r[8]; // trailing
// RUN: }' | nsl-fmt --stdin | FileCheck %s
// CHECK: /* hdr */
// CHECK-NEXT: reg q[8];
// CHECK: reg r[8]; // trailing
